
Usage of bare git dotfiles:

    https://developer.atlassian.com/blog/2016/02/best-way-to-store-dotfiles-git-bare-repo/
    https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=11071754

```
zsh
git clone --separate-git-dir=~/.dotfiles.git path/to/git ~/dotfiles-git
cp ~/dotfiles-git/.gitmodules ~/.gitmodules
source ~/dotfiles-git/.omz.custom/dotfiles.zsh
dotfiles
git config --local core.worktree $HOME
rm -rf submodules/paths/if/necessary ## cat .gitmodules
git submodules init
git submodules update
git config --local status.showUntrackedFiles no
git status -sb
...
dotfiles
```
